          "process_md": "> **Registration Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** Visit the official website: [http://gssyguj.in](https://gssyguj.in/).\n**Step 2:** Register online using the 18-digit CTS Aadhaar UDI number.\n**Step 3:** Provide mobile number, verify using OTP, and set a password to complete registration.\n> **Application Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** Log in using the registered Aadhaar number and password.\n**Step 2:** Fill out the online application form carefully, including personal details, school details (UDISE number), category (SC/ST/OBC/General/EWS), and residence type (Urban/Rural).\n**Step 3:** Upload the required documents including caste certificate (if applicable).\n**Step 4:** Preview the form, save and submit it online.\n**Step 5:** Take a printout of the submitted form for future reference.\n**Step 6:** Regularly check the website and registered mobile number for updates and merit list announcements.\n> **Contact Us:**\n\n**Commissioner of Schools**\n**Address:** Block-9, 1 st floor, J.M.Bhavan, Old sachivalaya, Gandhinagar\n**Tel. no. :** 079-23254011\n**Other office:** 079-23254014\n**E-mail:** gssyguj@gmail.com\n<br>\n\n"
        }
